        <p><strong>A:</strong> Microsoft automatically removes parental controls and converts the account to an adult account. Your child can choose to remain in the family group or leave.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>Q: Can I monitor my child's WhatsApp, Snapchat, or TikTok?</h4>
        <p><strong>A:</strong> No. Microsoft Family Safety only tracks Microsoft ecosystem apps. Third-party social media apps are not monitored. Use DNS filtering to block inappropriate content, or use app-specific parental controls.</p>
