      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>Q: Does Microsoft Family work on Mac, Chromebook, or iPad?</h4>
        <p><strong>A:</strong> Partially. Full features only work on Windows 10/11 and Xbox. On iOS/Android, the Family Safety app provides location tracking and driving safety. macOS, iPadOS, and Chrome OS are not supported for screen time or content filtering.</p>
